data.description: Situated in the heart of Carolina Forest, this home is nestled within a secure gated community, making it an ideal haven for both families and retirees alike.  This immaculate, custom-built residence boasts five generously proportioned bedrooms, three elegantly appointed bathrooms, and lofty 9-foot ceilings throughout. Its serene location culminates in a peaceful cul-de-sac position, graced by a tranquil pond backdrop, offering the ultimate in natural beauty.  An added jewel to this remarkable home is the versatile bonus room/ mother in law suite located on the upper level, providing endless possibilities to cater to your unique needs.  The property features an oversized two-car garage, ensuring ample space for your vehicles and additional storage.  As a testament to the home owners commitment to quality, a brand-new roof, installed by WeatherGuard on October 20, 2023, guarantees both peace of mind and lasting protection for years to come.  To Convey: Washer, Dryer, All Fridges
